messages.message:
@jack.robbins one of the client is looking for an update.
https://instabase.atlassian.net/browse/EPD-3651

Unfortunately I don't have any timeline updates on that particular request, but we are planning to start development on https://instabase.atlassian.net/browse/EPD-3279 this quarter, which is related and will establish some design patterns.

If their use-case is copying large classes _within the same project_, it may be possible to explore API-based options with soleng support.
@jack.robbins they're our partner, they don't have Soleng assigned.
